  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project partners - UVAN Ltd and Firmenich, (but formerly the Danish partner was Danisco A/S) - intend to secure long-term sustainable vanilla production and improve the quality of the cured vanilla beans purchased by Firmenich in Uganda from UVAN Ltd.
To achieve these aims, improvements are necessary at the curing station. The training of curing station workers and the farmers that grow the vanilla beans also need to be upgraded.</narrative>
